'''Jonathan Hales''' co-wrote the script for [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']] with [[George Lucas]]. He worked with Lucas on the script's third draft.<ref>{{SWArchive|url=episode-ii/bts/profile/f20020115/indexp3.html|text=George Lucas Interview - The Story Comes First: Scripting and Casting}}</ref> He had previously worked with Lucas on ''[[W:c:indianajones:The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles|The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles]]''.

